                <div class="space-y-8 text-on-surface-variant font-body-md text-lg leading-[1.8]">
                    <p>Founded in 1999, SteelCrest Roofing began with a single mission: to provide the most durable and aesthetically refined roofing solutions for Austin's most prestigious estates and commercial landmarks.</p>
                    <p>Our values are rooted in the principles of structural integrity and transparent communication. Every project we undertake is a testament to our philosophy that a roof is not just a protective barrier, but a crowning architectural statement.</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-12 pt-8">
                        <div>
                            <span class="block font-display-lg text-5xl text-secondary counter" data-target="25">0+</span>
                            <span class="font-label-caps text-on-background/60 text-sm mt-2 block">Years of Experience</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="block font-display-lg text-5xl text-secondary counter" data-target="500">0+</span>
                            <span class="font-label-caps text-on-background/60 text-sm mt-2 block">Projects Completed</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 animate-on-scroll stagger-item" style="--order: 1;">
                <div class="relative group">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-4 border-2 border-secondary/20 translate-x-4 translate-y-4 -z-10 group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500 rounded-sm"></div>
                    <img class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover shadow-xl rounded-sm" alt="Professional roofing team installing premium dark shingles on Austin modern luxury home" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCgOx0sPrZq58jFni4_2SNBbZMUHyzsqQ8TA9jhFI1yVcbPtdfO5965DgmuZFP-8bpkxcuwyU4q0BC9bxGDA95u20B6ZUl2F9D7zTu776RQwtO0hbBGhz7VV8ztvqFhi_-ZXdYYYYH-N7a9DcOeMJOfXJv8Q3knDdqwII6561coQmvF1QRnwIR-pbWabnwTA5BRdWTx_Coh6m5wmwJrZNJ39P4aKLpgGlzdVe2u0cAVH4R0vjnBbmPfbg5Q2miaqRHrZltcTb07Th6i"/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- The SteelCrest Core Standards -->
<section class="py-section-gap bg-[#170C79] text-on-primary overflow-hidden">
